This directory is intended for project specific (private) libraries.
PlatformIO will compile them to static libraries and link into executable file.

The source code of each library should be placed in an own separate directory
("lib/your_library_name/src" folder) or a single file if the library is small.

PlatformIO will find the lib_extra_dirs variable in the top-level
platformio.ini file, using the `lib_extra_dirs` option to specify additional
locations for project-specific (private) libraries.

More information about PlatformIO Library Dependency Finder
- https://docs.platformio.org/page/librarymanager/ldf.html
